{"about_the_game":"Based on the classic bluff turn-based card game Bullsh*t, <br><strong>BULLCRAP</strong> is a game of lies, poop and deceit!<br><br>Play online with up to <strong>Four</strong> of your friends,<br>or play solo over <strong>6 Chapters</strong> of increasingly fun and challenging levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet <strong>Bucky</strong> the Bull and his untrustworthy lying farmyard friends!<br></li><li>Call <strong>&quot;BULLCRAP!&quot;</strong> to punish your friends!<br></li><li>Bend the rules of the game with <strong>Wild Cards</strong>!<br></li><li>Combine Wild Cards to <strong>Power Up</strong>!<br></li><li>Watch as Bucky gets <strong>Angrier</strong> and angrier!<br></li><li>Unleash <strong>Chaos</strong> upon the farm!<br></li><li>Things are going to get messy, it\u2019s time to play <strong>Dirty</strong>!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2>The goal of the game is to get rid of <strong>all</strong> of your cards.<br><br>You can do this by <strong>Lying</strong>, or telling the <strong>Truth</strong>!<br>When you think someone is lying, call <strong>&quot;BULLCRAP!&quot;</strong>.<br>If they were lying, they have to pick up <strong>all </strong> the cards.<br>However, if they are telling the truth <strong>you</strong> pick up all the cards.<br>The <strong>Risk</strong> is all part of the fun!<br><br><strong>Wild Cards</strong> add an element of chaos to the game, <br>meaning you'll need to switch up your strategy and learn new tricks!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1712223587","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174200/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1712223587","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174200/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1712223587","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/21742